iZombie -LRB- stylized as iZOMBiE -RRB- is an American television series developed by Rob Thomas and Diane Ruggiero-Wright for The CW .
It is a loose adaptation of the comic book series of the same name created by Chris Roberson and Michael Allred , and published by DC Comics under their Vertigo imprint .
The series premiered on March 17 , 2015 .
The series was renewed for a second season , which premiered October 6 , 2015 , and ran for 19 episodes .
On March 11 , 2016 , The CW renewed the series for a third season of 13 episodes , which premiered on April 4 , 2017 .
On May 10 , 2017 , The CW renewed the series for a fourth season .